review_blob: You can smell the heat and I like heat.  My first thought was I love this, had a hot sauce aftertaste.  As I drink more I have decided it is just different.  Switching to something else.  Everybody should have one.  After that its up to you.
beer_name: Fort Collins Red Hot Chili Porter

review_blob: Quite possibly the best beer I have ever tasted.  Van Steenberg got sour perfect !!!!!!!
Very nice.  One of my favorite porters I have tasted in a while.  Was excited when i first tasted it.
Very smooth, love the aroma.  You can really taste the vanilla.  I would recomend it.
